{"tid":1693982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"修例風波：3內地漢在港與示威者衝突 網民奉為英雄","createTime":"2019-11-05T01:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T04:09:33.000Z","uid":56881,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"046469d059cb11f306fd9b7f65c226bab51ea057","tid":1693982,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-3-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%BC%A2%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%A5%89%E7%82%BA%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84-235702876.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-3-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%2589%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584-235702876.html&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=65c0118e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-3-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%BC%A2%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%A5%89%E7%82%BA%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84-235702876.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KIQ95mInFD.XqxS2zGlY9w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-11/c0e3e400-ff5e-11e9-b523-e59971320a65\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKIQ95mInFD.XqxS2zGlY9w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-11%2Fc0e3e400-ff5e-11e9-b523-e59971320a65&h=300b90c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當日其中一名內地漢揮舞雨傘，與示威者糾纏（左圖）。他們目前已返回內地，拍片報平安（右圖）。（何天成攝／互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n3名內地男子上周六（2日）在香港的示威地區，與多人發生肢體衝突，有關影片在網上流傳，引起內地網民熱議，讚揚他們是「英雄」。3人自稱「東北3兄弟」，早前已回到內地後，並在微博上傳影片短片報平安。<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳的片段可見，當時3人在彌敦道尖沙咀港鐵站附近與示威者發生肢體衝突，被示威者包圍毆打，其中一人面部被塗黑，另一人揮動雨傘還擊。期間有示威者用廣東話向他們大叫「滾回中國」，最終示威者散去。有指衝突原因是有人被懷疑舉機拍攝示威者容貌。<br />\n<br />\n短片引起內地網民熱烈議論，有網民更聲稱，要組隊來到香港「打廢青」，更揚言，「警察揍不了的，我們大陸民眾可以去教育教育！」。<br />\n<br />\n3人目前已返回內地，並在周一（4日）拍攝短片上傳微博報平安：「我們現在已安全離港，傷勢不重，支持香港警察，希望香港早日回復往日繁榮，香港挺住！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好打啦唔好打啦夠啦夠啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cff7de18601b5758e4563cfbc69416e1dc0e554","tid":1693982,"uid":318362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:02:59.000Z","msg":"來來來，支那粉蛆見一隻劏一隻&hellip;&hellip;千祈唔好"},{"pid":"f10e03a4150e6d71a55470655b40594e53219491","tid":1693982,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你老母 影哂片打人仲要自認打人 咁都唔做野<br />\n無片影到打人班手足就日日比人捉"},{"pid":"0960847f9acdcbeb01df521df3b9b1123e00c1c4","tid":1693982,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"點解唔打柒佢地"},{"pid":"d0930a3d0fa1ec84dac8e3a45b1ec3ee0ab3e98f","tid":1693982,"uid":129848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:11:14.000Z","msg":"咁聽話滾回中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做咩唔為國捐軀"},{"pid":"ee25d891b7ddeca52e547fce91e696ebe32b15aa","tid":1693982,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"好呀 快啲嚟<br />\n差唔多5個月<br />\n我1隻神獸都未親眼見過<br />\n好撚遺憾"},{"pid":"37bf9c6cff1131a5e897ffdb2965868b528b75e5","tid":1693982,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T02:12:44.000Z","msg":"唔好用國旗打人啦<br />\n陣間我哋騎劫咗五星旗嘅意義就唔好啦<br />\n中國旗侮辱中國人冇旗用㗎啦"},{"pid":"94f57f2be7b7885f655122381daf67924375e86f","tid":1693982,"uid":286897,"like":